data.title: PSN Account ID by FlipScreen Games
data.meta_description: Find your PSN Account ID correctly encoded for use with Chiaki, PSPlay, and other PS4 and PS5 remote play apps.
data.text:
Enter the username (Online ID) of the account you'd like to lookup and click submit to search PSN.

Note: Your privacy settings need to allow for "Anyone" to find you in search. You can change this back once you have your Account ID.
